Author: excelzombie
Text: I thought this said mcdonalds and was like 'alright.....this timeline is getting to crazy' if they started serving ramen in a cup everywhere can you imagine ooo lordy.

Author: superschuch
Text: Maybe try the McDougal's noodle cups next time. There's different flavors like pad Thai, Miso, etc. They are 200 calls or less, made with better ingredients than cup o noodles.
